				{% if current_lang == "en-gb" %}We make only those fertilizers that we are proud of. At the heart of WONDER products - quality raw materials from the world's best manufacturers. We take into account the specifics of any soil, their need for macro-and micronutrients.{% endif %}
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-3 col-xs-3 wonder-is-col-sm-3">
